85
00:04:40,270 --> 00:04:41,190
But she is.

86
00:04:41,890 --> 00:04:43,350
We'll make up a statement later

87
00:04:43,350 --> 00:04:44,540
and get her fingerprints.

88
00:04:44,540 --> 00:04:46,400
Then she'll be one no matter what.

89
00:04:46,470 --> 00:04:47,190
Sir.

90
00:04:54,260 --> 00:04:55,130
Mr. Kang.

91
00:04:56,580 --> 00:04:58,620
Why me?

92
00:04:58,650 --> 00:05:00,310
Because you're cruel enough.

93
00:05:01,320 --> 00:05:02,850
And you have no choice.

94
00:05:03,230 --> 00:05:04,500
You can only follow my instructions

95
00:05:04,500 --> 00:05:05,760
