104
00:05:26,270 --> 00:05:28,470
If I really wanted to teach you a lesson...

105
00:05:28,470 --> 00:05:29,470
All these years,

106
00:05:30,710 --> 00:05:33,659
among the cases you solved for political achievements,

107
00:05:33,659 --> 00:05:35,720
