108
00:05:37,880 --> 00:05:39,370
If I really become your enemy,

109
00:05:39,370 --> 00:05:41,630
can your friends in Nanjing protect you?

110
00:05:44,730 --> 00:05:45,960
Back to the topic,

111
00:05:47,210 --> 00:05:48,390
if you take this job,

112
00:05:49,290 --> 00:05:51,020
we'll be on the same ship again.

113
00:05:51,940 --> 00:05:54,180
Focus on making money for us.

114
00:05:55,310 --> 00:05:56,510
If you do well

115
00:05:56,990 --> 00:05:58,650
and the higher-ups are happy,

116
00:05:59,130 --> 00:06:01,060
you'll still have a bright future.

117
00:06:09,630 --> 00:06:12,610
It seems Nanjing has been rotten from the root.

118
00:06:15,260 --> 00:06:16,110
Of course.

119
00:06:17,910 --> 00:06:19,250
How else would

120
00:06:19,720 --> 00:06:21,190
such a strong and well-equipped government

121
00:06:21,190 --> 00:06:23,430
lose so spectacularly in Jiangxi?

122
00:06:24,590 --> 00:06:25,990
In troubled times,

123
00:06:26,580 --> 00:06:29,640
you should leave a way out for yourself and your family.

124
00:06:31,960 --> 00:06:33,840
Do you know how much gold

125
00:06:33,880 --> 00:06:36,680
is traded out of Nanjing's black market every day?

126
00:06:37,580 --> 00:06:38,780
When doomsday comes,

127
00:06:38,860 --> 00:06:40,820
the rich ones will be the first to run.

128
00:06:40,820 --> 00:06:41,620
And you want us

129
00:06:42,030 --> 00:06:43,090
to be the good guys?

130
00:06:43,600 --> 00:06:45,110
Quit joking.

131
00:06:50,090 --> 00:06:50,650
Sir...

132
00:07:07,340 --> 00:07:09,220
I'll be in your care, Mr. Kang.

133
00:07:11,890 --> 00:07:13,290
That's more like it.

134
00:07:16,570 --> 00:07:17,570
Work hard.

135
00:07:19,030 --> 00:07:20,030
Do a good

136
00:07:20,290 --> 00:07:21,140
