137
00:07:22,110 --> 00:07:24,110
I'll personally celebrate for you.

138
00:07:27,590 --> 00:07:28,150
Sir.

139
00:07:29,030 --> 00:07:30,580
I'm sorry about earlier.

140
00:07:37,100 --> 00:07:37,890
I'm sorry.

141
00:07:39,300 --> 00:07:40,470
I'm sorry, Meijuan.

142
00:07:41,670 --> 00:07:42,370
I'm sorry.

143
00:07:42,780 --> 00:07:43,610
No.

144
00:07:44,570 --> 00:07:45,750
You can't do this.

145
