You can't do this.

146
00:07:56,150 --> 00:07:56,840
Come in.

147
00:08:02,160 --> 00:08:03,560
Sir, you wanted to see me?

148
00:08:04,580 --> 00:08:06,310
Have you met Jinzhen recently?

149
00:08:06,440 --> 00:08:07,800
No. What's wrong, Sir?

150
00:08:07,900 --> 00:08:09,730
I saw you take her away at the banquet that day.

151
00:08:09,730 --> 00:08:11,190
You talked for a long time.

152
00:08:12,000 --> 00:08:12,930
Are the two of you

153
00:08:13,530 --> 00:08:14,280
hiding a secret?

154
00:08:14,280 --> 00:08:15,190
No, no.

155
00:08:15,500 --> 00:08:17,820
We were just chatting.

156
00:08:17,930 --> 00:08:19,130
No need to be nervous.

157
00:08:19,570 --> 00:08:21,310
You're around the same age as her.

158
00:08:21,310 --> 00:08:22,250
I think the two of you can

159
00:08:22,250 --> 00:08:24,010
communicate and meet more often.

160
00:08:24,010 --> 00:08:25,280
You can also

161
00:08:25,790 --> 00:08:26,590
help me

162
00:08:28,110 --> 00:08:29,970
talk to her about certain things.

163
00:08:30,140 --> 00:08:30,990
Such as, Sir?

164
00:08:33,549 --> 00:08:35,840
I suspected that she was part of the Communist Party.

165
00:08:35,840 --> 00:08:36,840
This matter

166
00:08:37,169 --> 00:08:39,210
has created a rift between us.

167
00:08:39,669 --> 00:08:41,669
I'm in no position to talk to her now.

168
00:08:42,309 --> 00:08:43,140
Your sister-in-law

169
00:08:43,140 --> 00:08:44,370
knows nothing about this.

170
00:08:44,370 --> 00:08:46,070
It's pointless to talk to her about it.

171
00:08:46,070 --> 00:08:47,730
So talk to Jinzhen in my stead.

172
00:08:48,290 --> 00:08:49,880
The war between the two parties is coming.

173
00:08:49,880 --> 00:08:51,760
