175
00:08:53,220 --> 00:08:54,940
and her family in more trouble.

176
00:08:54,940 --> 00:08:55,750
Yes, Sir.

177
00:08:56,300 --> 00:08:57,620
-But I…
-But what?

178
00:08:57,840 --> 00:08:59,170
You're in finance.

179
00:08:59,420 --> 00:09:01,320
Communication ability is very important.

180
00:09:01,320 --> 00:09:02,110
Talk to her more.

181
00:09:02,110 --> 00:09:03,310
Treat it as practice.

182
00:09:03,650 --> 00:09:04,210
Yes.

