Are you free tonight?

187
00:09:17,900 --> 00:09:19,790
Can I invite you to dinner?

188
00:09:23,330 --> 00:09:23,980
Sure.

189
00:09:24,600 --> 00:09:25,680
Can you cook?

190
00:09:27,400 --> 00:09:28,650
I'm tired of the food outside.

191
00:09:28,650 --> 00:09:31,110
I want to eat some home-cooked dishes today.

192
00:09:31,820 --> 00:09:32,460
Okay.

193
00:09:40,100 --> 00:09:41,220
Do you want a taxi?

194
00:09:41,660 --> 00:09:43,470
No, I want to take a walk.

195
00:09:49,280 --> 00:09:50,740
Watch out for the puddles.

196
00:09:50,760 --> 00:09:51,760
