197
00:09:52,210 --> 00:09:53,570
Miss, you're so pretty.

198
00:09:53,590 --> 00:09:54,590
Wei, you're back.

199
00:09:55,020 --> 00:09:55,880
This is my friend.

200
00:09:55,880 --> 00:09:57,060
She's so pretty.

201
00:09:57,120 --> 00:09:58,250
This woman won't do.

202
00:09:58,310 --> 00:09:59,100
Why not?

203
00:09:59,600 --> 00:10:00,800
Wei can't afford her.

204
00:10:00,870 --> 00:10:01,580
Why not?

205
00:10:02,120 --> 00:10:04,080
Did you see her shoes?

206
00:10:04,110 --> 00:10:06,020
Those shoes are worth your rent for six months.

207
00:10:06,020 --> 00:10:07,020
Wei, you're back.

208
00:10:10,020 --> 00:10:11,090
Wei, you're back.

209
00:10:11,870 --> 00:10:12,520
Ms. Zhou.

210
00:10:12,910 --> 00:10:13,790
Who is she?

211
00:10:14,020 --> 00:10:15,340
My friend, Miss Shen.

212
00:10:15,750 --> 00:10:17,010
My landlady, Ms. Zhou.

213
00:10:17,360 --> 00:10:18,440
Hello, Ms. Zhou.

214
00:10:18,470 --> 00:10:19,230
