215
00:10:19,230 --> 00:10:19,950
Hello.

216
00:10:20,790 --> 00:10:21,550
Hello.

217
00:10:21,630 --> 00:10:22,590
Hello.

218
00:10:24,140 --> 00:10:25,410
We'll go in now.

219
00:10:29,370 --> 00:10:30,370
Wei, you're back.

220
00:10:30,550 --> 00:10:30,990
Wei.

221
00:10:31,010 --> 00:10:31,410
Hello.

222
00:10:31,440 --> 00:10:32,440
You're so pretty.

223
00:10:35,070 --> 00:10:35,930
Don't worry.

224
00:10:36,190 --> 00:10:38,070
It won't work.

225
00:10:38,100 --> 00:10:38,760
What? Why?

226
00:10:38,790 --> 00:10:40,240
It's so lively here.

227
00:10:40,270 --> 00:10:42,550
If Wei really liked this girl,

228
00:10:42,570 --> 00:10:44,090
would he bring her here?

229
00:10:44,250 --> 00:10:46,360
He would have brought her to a fancy place

230
00:10:46,360 --> 00:10:48,480
for some coffee and Western food.

231
00:10:48,660 --> 00:10:49,300
He brought her here instead.

232
00:10:49,300 --> 00:10:50,370
Do you know what it means?

233
00:10:50,370 --> 00:10:51,370
What does it mean?

234
00:10:51,400 --> 00:10:53,060
He's indirectly telling her,

235
00:10:53,120 --> 00:10:54,960
"Sorry, I have no money."

236
00:10:54,990 --> 00:10:56,300
"I'm not a good match for you."

237
00:10:56,300 --> 00:10:58,130
He's rejecting her this way.

238
00:10:58,850 --> 00:11:00,040
He could have just said that.

239
00:11:00,040 --> 00:11:00,880
That's right.

240
00:11:01,710 --> 00:11:03,310
You can't say that directly.

241
00:11:03,390 --> 00:11:04,060
"I'm sorry."

242
00:11:04,060 --> 00:11:05,050
"We're not suitable for each other."

243
00:11:05,050 --> 00:11:06,340
If he said that, he'd be doomed.

244
00:11:06,340 --> 00:11:08,340
If this girl is rich,

245
00:11:08,360 --> 00:11:09,870
she just needs to call the bank

246
00:11:09,870 --> 00:11:11,400
and Wei will be unemployed.

247
00:11:11,820 --> 00:11:12,300
Right.

248
00:11:12,320 --> 00:11:12,760
Right?

249
00:11:12,800 --> 00:11:13,600
Right.

250
00:11:15,030 --> 00:11:16,060
That scary?

251
00:11:17,030 --> 00:11:18,230
But this young man

252
00:11:18,860 --> 00:11:19,720
is quite smart.

253
00:11:26,740 --> 00:11:27,460
Well,

254
00:11:27,780 --> 00:11:29,380
I'm not very good at cooking.

255
00:11:29,540 --> 00:11:30,660
Please make do.

256
00:11:31,430 --> 00:11:33,450
It's okay. Thank you.

257
00:11:33,660 --> 00:11:34,990
You made so many dishes.

258
00:11:49,550 --> 00:11:52,080
