259
00:11:52,430 --> 00:11:53,830
Don't cook next time.

260
00:11:54,270 --> 00:11:55,400
It's a waste of food.

261
00:11:59,040 --> 00:12:00,040
I'm sorry.

262
00:12:01,440 --> 00:12:02,160
From now on,

263
00:12:02,430 --> 00:12:03,780
I won't cook again.

264
00:12:05,210 --> 00:12:05,880
It's okay.

265
00:12:06,540 --> 00:12:08,220
Tell me, what's the matter?

266
00:12:14,900 --> 00:12:16,830
Did my brother ask you to come to me?

267
00:12:18,750 --> 00:12:19,350
Yes.

268
00:12:20,510 --> 00:12:22,110
Harmony brings prosperity.

269
00:12:22,120 --> 00:12:23,050
Don't blame him.

270
00:12:23,310 --> 00:12:23,910
After all,

271
00:12:26,580 --> 00:12:29,180
you're really working for the Community part.

272
00:12:33,340 --> 00:12:34,800
The matter between my brother and me

273
00:12:34,800 --> 00:12:36,400
is not as simple as you think.

274
00:12:36,500 --> 00:12:37,750
It's hard to explain.

275
00:12:42,150 --> 00:12:44,410
You said I'm part of the Communist Party.

276
00:12:44,700 --> 00:12:47,340
Do you know anything about the Communist Party?

277
00:12:47,340 --> 00:12:48,220
Not at all.

278
00:12:48,770 --> 00:12:50,970
Your brother never mentioned it to you?

279
00:12:51,310 --> 00:12:52,340
No.

280
00:12:52,990 --> 00:12:54,100
But I think

281
00:12:54,540 --> 00:12:56,270
he didn't want to implicate me.

282
00:12:57,050 --> 00:12:58,310
Have you ever wondered

283
00:12:58,940 --> 00:13:01,470
why your brother joined the Communist Party?

284
00:13:02,420 --> 00:13:03,260
I thought about it.

285
00:13:03,260 --> 00:13:04,140
Why?

286
00:13:08,840 --> 00:13:09,520
Forget it.

287
00:13:09,760 --> 00:13:10,930
I'd better not say it.

288
00:13:10,930 --> 00:13:12,660
I'm afraid you'll be angry.

289
00:13:12,680 --> 00:13:14,600
Just tell me. I promise I won't be.

290
00:13:20,540 --> 00:13:21,470
My brother

291
00:13:22,240 --> 00:13:23,920
